# Deepfake intermediates and derivatives — never commit, even to private repos.
# See docs/case-study.md "Distribution" + "What this clip is not".
# Original CC-licensed source media (face-source.jpg, face-target.mp4) IS allowed.
/data/case-study/sources/swapped-raw*.mp4
/data/case-study/sources/face-target-720p.mp4
/data/case-study/sources/fake-audio.wav

